title: TOWO Wooden Food Cutting Game - Wooden Play Food Fruit Toys and Vegetables Cutting Toys for 3 Years Old
features: Fine wooden fruits cutting toy with 5 types of real size wooden fruit which are pear, apple, kiwi, orange and lemon. One of popular wooden cutting food fruit and veg toys for kids

Each wooden fruit are connected with magnets in the middle for easy slicing and assembling. It is an ideal wooden food toy for pretend food play or as wooden kitchen toys accessories and role play toy for kids; for practicing hand and eye coordination, improving concentration and also great for encouraging early interest in eating healthy fruit

Comes with a wooden knife and a multi-purpose wooden box that can be used as a storage box and a cutting board at the same time. The fruit pieces can be a great way to introduce the concept of part, whole and fractions to children, and they will surely enjoy cutting the fruits with the wooden knife
Suitable for 3 years and older. It is always advisable that an adult to supervise and enjoy the interaction of children with this wooden food toy

Safe and environmentally friendly: it is made of sustainable wood with environmentally friendly and non-toxic paints. It conforms to EC EN71, ASTM F963 and CPSIA toys safety Standards; being tested and certified by International Accredited Labs.
description: Fine wooden cutting toy for children with knife and five popular fruits and a multi-purpose wooden box that can be used as a cutting tray and storage. The wooden fruit pieces are connected with magnets for easily sliced in halves and assembled. Great for encouraging early interest in healthy fruits as well as teaching manual dexterity. Many pieces are great way to introduce the concept of part, whole and fractions. "Toys of Wood Oxford" or "TOWO” is known for its fine quality, fun and educational multifunctional wooden toys. We pride ourselves on providing good quality products and first class customer service. We hope our products will bring lots of fun and enjoyment to your children and family.
